data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home with 2 bedrooms down. Situated opposite the community splash pad, a walking trail, & greenbelt, this home has a perfect location. Walking in you are greeted by a grand vaulted ceiling dining room which exudes class & comfort. The beautiful wood floors guide you through the open floor plan past the second bedroom downstairs and into your oversized kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of storage, and high-end appliances. The kitchen overlooks the breakfast nook & spacious living room with a lovely fireplace. The primary bedroom is large and the bathroom has double vanities, a deep tub, & a walk-in shower, and a walk-in closet. Upstairs is a kid's dream with 2 additional bedrooms, a huge playroom, and a flex space for crafts, media room, office, or exercise room. This home is great for those who enjoy space & storage & enjoy entertaining and showcasing their new home. Don't miss your chance to call this one yours! 2023-10-07
